{"tid":2315023,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"AV界灰姑娘相澤南12件往事 人氣墊底翻身成黑馬影后背後充滿洋蔥","createTime":"2020-12-07T02:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T04:32:18.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4b1bba9fafabc0239dbd7b876725a79242241022","tid":2315023,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T02:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201203/411236841845428224873201.jpeg/bUGoI9OBGsr4_XVClt2aqqOx_GrvoZoO3nqg2956oNs?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201203%2F411236841845428224873201.jpeg%2FbUGoI9OBGsr4_XVClt2aqqOx_GrvoZoO3nqg2956oNs%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=f3709efc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年AV影后相澤南，在頒獎台上啜泣，事前沒有人想到她會勝出，連她自己也沒想到會有這一日。這位AV界公認的灰姑娘，事業一路坎坷，被好友出賣、經理人多次病倒、人氣低迷，她是如何在多次困境低谷成AV影后？<br />\n<br />\n對比出道就萬眾矚目的女星，相澤南可謂是草根中的草根，在跟事業中的伯樂，傳說中的人物「社長」相遇之後，就一路互相扶持，不斷起起落落落落落落。每一次轉機的出現，背後卻都有一個命運的玩笑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n社長在相澤南奪下影后之後，發了一篇長文《相澤南的灰姑娘傳奇》，相澤南的往事才正式為人所知。這個「社長」到底是何方神聖？相澤南在至今短短幾年的女優生涯中，又經歷過甚麼？"},{"pid":"1edd7bc7222b8113efad96ee1b0bad68773764f0","tid":2315023,"uid":50041,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T02:43:41.000Z","msg":"真係唔係好理解到點解會叫自己條女拍AV<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f677d47c8f0ca95f8f609bf257927fc7da77f68","tid":2315023,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T02:43:41.000Z","msg":"社長唔係佢條仔兼死埋咩 ??"},{"pid":"968785fba4cbe6890029da1b916d3dc520aa7050","tid":2315023,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T02:43:55.000Z","msg":"想知再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62fa8f6e10a0723860bece8725fc9306e2eb2840","tid":2315023,"uid":124655,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"1edd7bc7222b8113efad96ee1b0bad68773764f0